@startuml sequence-google
title MONSITE — Connexion via Google (OAuth2 + PKCE)

autonumber

actor "Utilisateur" as User
participant "Navigateur" as Browser
participant "MONSITE\n(Client App)" as Monsite
participant "Google\n(Authorization Server)" as GoogleAuth
participant "Google\n(Resource Server)" as GoogleRes

User -> Browser: Clique "Se connecter avec Google"
Browser -> Monsite: GET /api/auth/google/authorize
activate Monsite
Monsite -> Monsite: Génère state (CSRF) + PKCE\n(code_verifier, code_challenge = SHA256(verifier))
Monsite -> Browser: 302 Redirect vers Google\n+ Set-Cookie monsite_oauth_state\n(signé HMAC, HttpOnly, SameSite=Lax, TTL 10 min)
deactivate Monsite

Browser -> GoogleAuth: GET /o/oauth2/v2/auth\n?client_id&redirect_uri&response_type=code\n&scope=openid email profile\n&state&code_challenge&code_challenge_method=S256
activate GoogleAuth
GoogleAuth -> User: Affiche l'écran de connexion / consentement Google
User -> GoogleAuth: S'authentifie et autorise MONSITE
GoogleAuth -> Browser: 302 Redirect\n/api/auth/google/callback?code&state
deactivate GoogleAuth

Browser -> Monsite: GET /api/auth/google/callback?code&state
activate Monsite
Monsite -> Monsite: Vérifie signature + expiration du cookie state\ncompare state (timingSafeEqual)\nsupprime immédiatement monsite_oauth_state
Monsite -> GoogleAuth: POST /token\n(client_id, client_secret, code, redirect_uri,\ngrant_type=authorization_code, code_verifier)
activate GoogleAuth
GoogleAuth -> Monsite: 200 { access_token }
deactivate GoogleAuth

Monsite -> GoogleRes: GET /v1/userinfo\nAuthorization: Bearer access_token
activate GoogleRes
GoogleRes -> Monsite: 200 { sub, email, name, picture }
deactivate GoogleRes

Monsite -> Monsite: Construit le profil {provider, providerAccountId,\nemail, name, avatarUrl}\ncrée le cookie de session monsite_session
Monsite -> Browser: 307 Redirect /profile\n+ Set-Cookie monsite_session\n(signé HMAC, HttpOnly, SameSite=Lax, TTL 2h)
deactivate Monsite

Browser -> Monsite: GET /profile (cookie monsite_session)
Monsite -> Browser: 200 Page de profil (nom, courriel, avatar)

note over Monsite, GoogleAuth
  Si le callback est rejoué (double clic, retour arrière) : le cookie
  monsite_oauth_state a déjà été supprimé lors de la 1ère lecture,
  donc MONSITE rejette la requête lui-même (redirect /login?error=expired)
  avant toute nouvelle tentative d'échange de code.
end note

@enduml
